# Marathon bundle 9 (4b) — Playwright visual regression scratch dirs.
# Test output (videos, traces, diff PNGs from failed comparisons) and
# the html reporter dir are local-only — CI uploads them as artifacts
# on demand, the repo doesn't track them. Baselines under
# ``visual.spec.ts-snapshots/`` ARE committed (they ARE the spec).
.output/
.report/
# Operators running ``--update-snapshots`` locally on macOS/Windows
# generate platform-suffixed PNGs (e.g. login-chromium-darwin.png)
# that the spec never reads (snapshotPathTemplate strips the suffix).
# They are noise — keep them off git.
visual.spec.ts-snapshots/*-chromium-darwin.png
visual.spec.ts-snapshots/*-chromium-win32.png
